[[File:Nilo_Rodis-Jamero.jpg|thumb|250px|Nilo Rodis-Jamero.]]
'''Nilo Rodis-Jamero''' was the assistant art director of visual effects for [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']], and costume designer for [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]. He designed the [[Imperial Advisor/Legends|Imperial advisors]] and made a drawing that would go on to be [[Gial Ackbar]].<ref name="The Making of Return of the Jedi">''[[The Making of Return of the Jedi]]''</ref> {{Mediacat|imagecat=Images by Nilo Rodis-Jamero}}

